血浆抗体治疗投入新冠肺炎临床 专家：有效率在60%-90%。
Clinical Expert of Plasma Antibody Injection into Coronary Pneumonia: 60% -90% Effective.
瞿依贤2020-02-14 23:20。
Qu Yexian 2020-02-14 23: 20.
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
经济观察网 记者 瞿依贤2月13日晚间，中国医药集团下属公司中国生物宣布：在武汉地区实施了新冠肺炎康复者血浆采集，已成功制备出用于临床治疗的特免血浆，目前超过10名危重病人接受了新冠特免血浆治疗，患者接受治疗12至24小时后，实验室检测主要炎症指标明显下降，淋巴细胞比例上升，血氧饱和度、病毒载量等重点指标全面向好，临床体征和症状明显好转。
On the night of Feb. 13, China Biology, a subsidiary of the China Medical Group, announced that plasma collection of ex-Crowne Pneumonia patients in Wuhan has successfully prepared free plasma for clinical treatment. After 12 to 24 hours of treatment, laboratory tests of major inflammatory markers dropped significantly, lymphocyte rates increased, blood oxygen saturation, viral load and other key indicators improved significantly.
。
.
同样是13日晚间，武汉市金银潭医院院长张定宇在湖北省新冠疫情新闻发布会上表示，康复后的患者体内有大量的中和抗体来抵抗新冠病毒，呼吁康复期患者捐献血浆，共同拯救还在与病魔作斗争的病人。
Also on the night of the 13th, Zhang Dingyu, director of Wuhan Gold and Silver Pool Hospital, told a news conference in Hubei province that recovering patients had plenty of neutralizing antibodies to fight the new crown virus.
。
.
两则消息一出，受困的新冠肺炎患者看到了一线曙光：血浆抗体治疗可以降低危重症患者的病死率。
Two reports suggest a glimmer of hope in the beleaguered New Crown Pneumonia: Plasma antibody therapy can reduce the fatality rate in critically ill patients.
。
.
资本市场反应也尤为热烈，14日收盘，血制品概念股集体大涨，天坛生物（600161.SH）、卫光生物（002880.SZ）涨停，上海莱士（002252.SZ）涨幅超过7%，华兰生物（002007.SZ）、双林生物（000403.S）涨幅超过3%。
Capital markets were particularly responsive, with blood-products stocks surging, Titan (600161.SH), Wei Guangbiao (002880.SZ) trading, Shanghai (002252.SZ) rose more than 7%, Hua Lan biology (002007.SZ), Shuanglin biology (000403.S) rose more than 3%.
。
.
每人可采浆200-400毫升。
200-400 ml per person.
中国生物表示，已完成对部分康复者血浆的采集工作，开展新冠病毒特免血浆制品和特免球蛋白的制备。
China Biology said it had completed the collection of plasma from some recovered patients and initiated the preparation of new crown virus-free plasma products and immunoglobulin.
经过严格的血液生物安全性检测，病毒灭活，抗病毒活性检测等，已成功制备出用于临床治疗的特免血浆，在中国生物武汉生物制品研究所、国药集团武汉血液制品有限公司、武汉市江夏区第一人民医院、武汉血液中心、中科院武汉病毒研究所、中国食品药品检定研究院的合作下，投入临床救治重症患者。
After rigorous blood bio-safety testing, virus inactivation, antiviral activity testing, special plasma exemption has been successfully prepared for clinical treatment. In cooperation with Wuhan Biology Research Institute of China, Wuhan Haematology Group Wuhan Haematology Products Co. Ltd, Wuhan Jiangxia District First People's Hospital, Wuhan Blood Center, Wuhan Institute of Chinese Academy of Sciences Wuhan Virus Research Institute, China Food and Drug Verification Institute, have been put into clinical treatment.
。
.
2月8日，首期在江夏区第一人民医院开展了3名危重患者的新冠特免血浆治疗，目前连同后续医院治疗的危重病人超过了10人。
On 8 February, the first round of new plasma-free treatment for three critically ill patients was conducted at the First People's Hospital in Jiangxia District, and more than 10 critically ill patients are now being treated together with follow-up hospitals.
。
.
新冠特免血浆制品是由康复者捐献的含高效价新冠病毒特异性抗体的血浆，经过病毒灭活处理，并对抗新冠病毒中和抗体、多重病原微生物检测后制备而成，用于新冠肺炎危重患者的治疗。
The new crown plasma-free product is the plasma donated by the convalescent patients containing HPCV-specific antibodies, inactivated by virus and prepared against the neutralization antibodies and multiple pathogen microorganisms of the new crown virus for the treatment of critically ill patients with new crown pneumonia.
。
.
中国生物研发相关负责人表示，新冠病毒特免血浆的采集、制备和系列检测过程，具有良好的安全性，制备工艺成熟，所需时间短。
China's biological research and development, said the new cap virus special plasma collection, preparation and series of testing process, with good security, mature preparation process, the time required.
。
.
哈尔滨血液研究所所长、教授马军告诉经济观察网，血浆抗体治疗的技术已经有100多年历史，在2003年SARS的治疗中也用过，已经很成熟。
Professor Ma Jun, director of the Harbin Blood Institute, told the Economic Watch network that plasma antibody therapy has a 100-year history and is well established and used in the treatment of SARS in 2003.
在已经痊愈的新冠肺炎患者身上采浆，血浆中有抗新冠病毒抗体，也可能有多种综合性抗体，患者前期的症状越重，其抗体产生抗新冠病毒抗体越好。
The more severe the symptoms in the early stages, the better the antibodies produce antibodies to the new crown virus virus.
“经过分离血浆，再从血浆中分离出特异性抗体，再浓缩添加佐剂白蛋白制成纯抗新冠抗体，可输给重症新冠肺炎病人，有效率在60%-90%，这是在沒有特效药情况下的方法。
"Separation of plasma, separation of specific antibodies from plasma, and enrichment with adjuvant albumin to produce pure anti-Newcrown antibodies can be lost to patients with severe new crown pneumonia with an effective rate of 60% -90%, which is the method without specific drugs.
”。
"
“如果出院患者有抗新冠病毒抗体，每个人可以采浆200-400ml，最后混合多位出院患者的血浆，通过技术灭毒，得到综合抗体；再通过生物制剂的办法浓缩这些抗体，注射到重症患者体内。
"If the patient is discharged from the hospital with an antibody to the new crown virus, each person can take 200-400ml of plasma and finally mix the plasma of several discharged patients to obtain a comprehensive antibody through technical sterilization; then concentrate these antibodies by means of biological agents and inject them into patients with severe illnesses.
”马军说，具体的注射量要视具体情况而定。
Ma said the amount of the injection would depend on the circumstances.
。
.
一万多重症患者。
More than 10,000 seriously ill.
截至2月13日24时，除港澳台外全国现有确诊病例55748例，其中重症病例10204例，累计治愈出院病例6723例。
As of 2400 hours on February 13, there were 55,748 confirmed cases in China, including 10,204 cases of serious illness and 6,723 cases of discharge.
血浆抗体治疗，能成为现在一万多重症患者的“最后一根救命稻草”吗？。
Can plasma antibody therapy be the "last straw" for more than 10, 000 critically ill patients?
2月14日，上海有28名新冠肺炎患者治愈出院，其中有6名患者主动表示愿意捐献血浆，帮助更多患者。
On February 14, 28 patients in Shanghai were cured of pneumonia, six of whom offered to donate blood plasma to help more patients.
。
.
国家卫生健康委专家组成员、上海市公共卫生临床中心党委书记卢洪洲在接受采访时表示，上海已经有一例患者正在准备用恢复期患者的血浆来进行治疗，详细方案已经制定完毕。
In an interview, Lu Hongzhou, a member of the group of experts from the National Health and Health Commission and party secretary of the Shanghai Public Health Clinical Center, said in an interview that a patient in Shanghai was already preparing a plasma treatment with convalescent patients and a detailed plan had been developed.
上海市公共卫生临床中心在市区门诊、金山本部两处都设置了出院患者的门诊随访，检测操作和血浆制备可以在随访时进行，等再过两个礼拜左右，刚刚治愈出院的患者身体已经完全康复，再请他们来捐献血浆。
The Shanghai Public Health Clinic Center has set up outpatient follow-up visits for discharged patients in both the downtown outpatient clinic and Jinshan headquarters. The test operation and plasma preparation can be carried out during the follow-up visit.
。
.
马军表示，捐献200-400毫升血浆对人体没有伤害，但不是所有治愈的患者体内都有抗新冠病毒抗体，也就是说，不是所有治愈患者的血浆都可以用来生产抗体制剂。
Ma said the donation of 200-400 milliliters of plasma was not harmful to humans, but not all patients who were cured had antibodies to the new crown virus, meaning that not all plasma from cured patients could be used to produce antibody preparations.
对于体内含有抗新冠病毒抗体的患者，治愈30天的时候是体内抗体浓度的峰值，“不过重症患者等不了30天，在病人恢复、病毒转阴后10-14天捐献，对捐献者和重症患者都比较好”。
For patients with antibodies to the new crown virus, the peak in antibody concentration was reached 30 days after treatment, "although patients with severe illness wait less than 30 days, and are better for donors and patients with severe illnesses after recovery and donation 10-14 days after the virus has passed."
。
.
北京一家三甲医院的血液内科主任医师告诉经济观察网，血浆抗体治疗目前的可操作性不是太强，主要还是血浆的量不够，“现在治愈的人太少”，而且还要看产生的抗体浓度，以及抗体活性。
The head physician at a Beijing-based Sanjia hospital told the Economic Watch network that plasma antibody therapy is not too maneuverable at the moment, mainly in insufficient amounts of plasma, "too few people are cured now," but also depending on the concentration of the antibody produced and antibody activity.
。
.
马军表示，即便接受血浆抗体治疗，也有15%的患者可能没有效果，但现在没有特效药，“血浆治疗是简易、安全、可能有效的办法，注射了以后抗体高了，靠自身的免疫杀死病毒，在没有办法的情况下，这是能使病人恢复的办法”。
Even with plasma antibody therapy, 15 percent of patients may not be effective, Ma said, but there is no specific drug. "Plasma therapy is a simple, safe and potentially effective way to kill the virus with your own immunity."
。
.
“生物制品灭活、灭毒以后，可以在较多病人身上使用”，不过如果要放开给所有重症患者，马军认为要通过伦理、做临床试验，先做少量病人，验证有效性后再来考虑。
"Biological products can be inactivated, sterilized, can be used on a larger number of patients," but if we want to release it to all seriously ill patients, Ma believes we should go through ethical, clinical trials, do a small number of patients, verify the validity before considering.
。
.
中央指导组医疗救治组专家、北京朝阳医院副院长童朝晖也表示，目前已经在恢复性血浆的治疗中看出好的苗头，未来再做进一步的观察。
Tong Chaohui, vice-dean of Beijing Chaoyang Hospital and expert of the Central Steering Group's medical treatment group, also said that good results had been seen in the treatment of restorative plasma, and further observations should be made in the future.
。
.
附：新冠肺炎康复者捐献血浆提示。
Note: Blood plasma was donated by patients recovering from Newcomial Pneumonia.
1、康复者捐献血浆需要有哪些条件？。
1. What are the conditions for a convalescent person to donate plasma?
中国生物：新冠肺炎康复者年龄在18-60周岁，确诊感染过新型冠状病毒，出院后目前身体状况较好，没有其他不适，并愿意捐献出自己的血浆帮助他人，请携带本人身份证和出院小结联系血浆捐献点献血浆。
Chinese Biology: The new coronavirus has been diagnosed in the 18-60 age group. After discharge from the hospital, the patient is in good health and has no other discomfort. He is willing to donate his own plasma to help others. Please bring your own identity card and discharge summary to the plasma donation point to offer plasma.
。
.
2、康复者捐献血浆有哪些流程？。
2. What are the procedures for the convalescent person to donate plasma?
中国生物：可拨打爱心热线预约捐献血浆事宜，在捐献点经过登记、健康征询、体格检查，献浆前可饮用适量的水和食物，符合要求进行血浆采集（约20-30分钟），献浆后休息30分钟后可离开捐献点。
Chinese Biology: You can make an appointment to donate plasma by calling the Heart Hotline. After registration, health consultation, medical examination, drinking water and food at the donation point, you can take blood plasma (about 20-30 minutes) according to the requirements, and you can leave the donation point after 30 minutes' rest.
。
.
3、康复者捐献血浆前有哪些注意事项？。
3, what matters needing attention before convalescent person donates plasma?
中国生物：康复者捐献血浆前感觉身体状况良好，没有身体不适。
Chinese Biology: The convalescent person feels well before donating plasma and has no discomfort.
前一天尽量清淡饮食，不吃高脂肪、高蛋白、高淀粉（肉类、蛋类、豆类、辛辣等）食物，晚上注意早些休息，早上起床后可吃一些粥类、清淡面条、包子、馒头等。
Try not to eat high-fat, high-protein, high starch (meat, eggs, beans, spicy and so on) food, pay attention to early rest in the evening, wake up in the morning can eat some porridge, light noodles, steamed bread and so on.
不能空腹献血浆，女性月经期内不能献血浆。
Do not offer plasma on an empty stomach. Women cannot offer plasma during menstruation.
。
.
4、康复者捐献血浆后有哪些注意事项？。
4, what matters needing attention after convalescent person donates plasma?
中国生物：康复者捐献血浆后注意按压穿刺点20-30分钟，不能揉按穿刺点，止血后方可去掉创可贴，注意针眼处清洁卫生，不可用水擦洗。
Chinese organism: After the convalescent person donates the plasma, pay attention to press puncture point 20-30 minutes, can not knead according to the puncture point, can remove the wound paste after stop bleeding, note the needle eye clean, not water scrub.
献浆当日适当休息，不做剧烈运动，献浆手臂不持重物。
Shooting day appropriate rest, do not do vigorous exercise, pulp arm does not hold heavy objects.
饮食方面和日常生活用餐一样，不能暴饮暴食，不能饮酒。
Eating like daily meals, do not overeat, do not drink alcohol.
保持健康的生活方式，间隔14天后可再次捐献血浆。
Maintain a healthy lifestyle and re-donate plasma after a 14-day interval.
。
.
